	var event = document.createEvent('customEvent');
	event.initCustomEvent('pageViewCall', true, true, {
		eventType: "pageLoad",
		pageName: "uhc:myuhc:home:redesign:home",
		siteSection1: "home",
		siteSection2: "redesign",
		siteSection3: "",
		lineOfBusiness: "e&i",
		promoTitles: "",
		pageLanguage: "en"
	});
	document.body.dispatchEvent(event);

	showHideLangToggle();
	var registerLink = inputs.HSID_DOMAIN_URL+'/protected/register'+registerNowQs;
	var signInLink = inputs.HSID_DOMAIN_URL+'/secure/authenticate'+registerNowQs;
	document.getElementById("register").href = registerLink;
	
	if(document.getElementById("registerbutton")!== null){
		document.getElementById("registerbutton").onclick = function (){
			newPreloginRegisterButtonLink();
			window.location.href = registerLink;
		};

		function newPreloginRegisterButtonLink(){
			
			var event = document.createEvent('customEvent')    
		    event.initCustomEvent('linkCall', true, true, {
		       eventType: "intLinkClick",
		       linkName: "register-button",
		       linkURL: registerLink
		   });
			document.body.dispatchEvent(event);
		}
	}

	if(document.getElementById("signInButton")!== null){
		document.getElementById("signInButton").onclick = function (){
			newPreloginSignInButtonLink();
			window.location.href = signInLink;
		};

		function newPreloginSignInButtonLink(){
			var event = document.createEvent('customEvent')    
		    event.initCustomEvent('linkCall', true, true, {
		       eventType: "intLinkClick",
		       linkName: "sign-in-button",
		       linkURL: signInLink
		   });
			document.body.dispatchEvent(event);	
		}		
	}

	function showHideLangToggle(){
		var url = document.URL;
		if(contains(url,'es-') || contains(url,'es.')){
			document.getElementById('spanish').style.display='none';
			document.getElementById('english').style.display='block';
		}else {
			document.getElementById('spanish').style.display='block';
			document.getElementById('english').style.display='none';
		}
	} 

	function contains(mainString,subString){
		if(mainString.indexOf(subString)==-1){
			return 0;
		}
		else if (mainString.indexOf(subString)!=-1 && mainString.indexOf(subString)>20){
			return 0;
		}
		else{
			return 1;
		}
	}


	function changeLanguageMyuhc(selectedValue){

		var sLinkURL = "https://"+'www.myuhc.com'+"/member/prewelcome.do?currentLanguageFromPreCheck="+selectedValue;
		var sLinkName = "view-english-site";
		if(selectedValue == 'es'){
			window.location = "https://"+'www.myuhc.com'+"/member/preNewLoginChangeLanguage.do?selectedLanguageFromNewPrelogin=es";
			sLinkURL = "https://"+'www.myuhc.com'+"/member/preNewLoginChangeLanguage.do?selectedLanguageFromNewPrelogin=es";
			sLinkName = "view-spanish-site";	
		}else {
			window.location = "https://"+'www.myuhc.com'+"/member/prewelcome.do?currentLanguageFromPreCheck="+selectedValue;
		}


		var event = document.createEvent('customEvent')    
	    event.initCustomEvent('linkCall', true, true, {
	       eventType: "intLinkClick",
	       linkName: sLinkName,
	       linkURL: sLinkURL
	   });
		document.body.dispatchEvent(event);	
		
	}

    margin-left: 0;

  }

@media screen and (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  .carousel-item {
    transition: none;
  }
}

.carousel-item.active,
.carousel-item-next,
.carousel-item-prev {
  display: block;
}

.carousel-item-next:not(.carousel-item-left),
.active.carousel-item-right {
  -ms-transform: translateX(100%);
      transform: translateX(100%);
}

.carousel-item-prev:not(.carousel-item-right),
.active.carousel-item-left {
  -ms-transform: translateX(-100%);
      transform: translateX(-100%);
}

  opacity: 0;
  transition-property: opacity;
  -ms-transform: none;
      transform: none;
}

  opacity: 1;
}

  z-index: 0;
  opacity: 0;
  transition: 0s 0.6s opacity;
}

  }

 * Float Labels
 * @version: 3.3.8
 * @author: Paul Ryley (http://geminilabs.io)
 * @url: https://pryley.github.io/float-labels.js
 * @license: MIT
 */
.fl-form .fl-wrap {
  position: relative;
  text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
}

.fl-form input.fl-input,
.fl-form select.fl-select,
.fl-form textarea.fl-textarea {
  width: 100%;
  outline: 0;
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.5;
  border-radius: 3px;
  border: 1px solid #dfdfdf;
  background-color: #fff;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}

.fl-form input.fl-input:-moz-placeholder,
.fl-form select.fl-select:-moz-placeholder,
.fl-form textarea.fl-textarea:-moz-placeholder {
  color: #bbb;
}

.fl-form input.fl-input::-moz-placeholder,
.fl-form select.fl-select::-moz-placeholder,
.fl-form textarea.fl-textarea::-moz-placeholder {
  color: #bbb;
}

.fl-form input.fl-input:-ms-input-placeholder,
.fl-form select.fl-select:-ms-input-placeholder,
.fl-form textarea.fl-textarea:-ms-input-placeholder {
  color: #bbb;
}

.fl-form input.fl-input::-webkit-input-placeholder,
.fl-form select.fl-select::-webkit-input-placeholder,
.fl-form textarea.fl-textarea::-webkit-input-placeholder {
  color: #bbb;
}

.fl-form select.fl-select {
  position: relative;
  color: #bbb;
  cursor: pointer;
  -webkit-appearance: none;
  -moz-appearance: none;
}

.fl-form select.fl-select::-ms-expand {
  display: none;
}

.fl-form .fl-is-active input.fl-input,
.fl-form .fl-is-active select.fl-select,
.fl-form .fl-is-active textarea.fl-textarea {
  color: #444;
  background-color: #fff;
  border-color: #dfdfdf;
}

.fl-form .fl-has-focus input.fl-input,
.fl-form .fl-has-focus select.fl-select,
.fl-form .fl-has-focus textarea.fl-textarea {
  background-color: #fff;
  border-color: #1976D2;
}

.fl-form label.fl-label {
  opacity: 0;
  visibility: hidden;
  display: block;
  position: absolute;
  top: -12px;
  left: 0;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1;
  color: #bbb;
  border-top-left-radius: 3px;
  transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;

function linksVariables(event){
 	 	var eventType = event.detail.eventType;
  /* common variables for page load and link call start*/
    s.prop25 = s.eVar25 = "D=pageName";
 	  s.eVar3 = s.prop1 ='D=g'
    s.prop12= window.location.hostname;
  	var language = event.detail.pageLanguage
    /* will remove us keyword in next release */
    s.prop71= (language != undefined) ? language +'-us'  : document.documentElement.lang+'-us';
    s.prop44 = window.location.search;
  	s.prop13= window.location.pathname;
  	s.eVar72 = _satellite.getVisitorId().getMarketingCloudVisitorID();
    s.prop2= s.version;
    var website = event.detail.website;
    s.eVar2 = (website != undefined) ? website : 'myuhc';
   /* common variables for page load and link call end*/
if (eventType == 'intLinkClick'){
    s.linkTrackVars = "eVar3,eVar40,eVar72,prop1,prop40,prop59,prop12,prop25,prop71,eVar72,prop44,prop13,prop17"
    var linkName = event.detail.linkName;
    var linkURL = event.detail.linkURL;
   	s.eVar40 = s.prop40 = s.prop17 = linkName;
    s.tl(this,'o',linkName);
  }else if (eventType == 'exitLinkClick'){
    s.linkTrackVars = "eVar3,prop1,prop65,eVar72,prop59,prop12,prop25,prop71,eVar72,prop44,prop13,prop17"
    var linkName = event.detail.linkName;
    var linkURL = event.detail.linkURL;
    s.prop65 = s.prop17 = linkName;
    s.prop59 = linkURL;
    s.tl(this,'e',linkURL);
  }else if (eventType == 'downloadLinkClick'){
    console.log('please assign variables for downloadLinkClick')
  }else if(eventType == 'formLinkClick'){
    s.linkTrackVars = "eVar3,eVar40,eVar72,prop1,prop40,prop59,prop12,prop25,prop71,eVar72,prop44,prop13,prop17"
		var linkName = event.detail.linkName;
		var formName = event.detail.formName;
    if(formName == "sign-in-form"){
     if(_satellite.settings.isStaging==true){
       s.sa('uhghsiddev,uhgoptumglobaldev,uhgmyuhcdev'); 
     } else { 
       s.sa('uhghsidprod,uhgoptumglobalprod,uhgmyuhcprod'); 
     }
   }
		s.eVar40 = s.prop40 = s.prop17 = linkName;
		s.tl(this,'o',linkName); 
  }
}
